Nature research paper: Structural basis for the conformational protection of nitrogenase from O2

https://go.nature.com/4aiD344

embeds.title: Structural basis for the conformational protection of nitrogenase from O2 - Nature
embeds.description: Cryo-electron microscopy of Azotobacter vinelandii FeSII–nitrogenase reveals a core complex of molybdenum–iron proteins (MoFePs), iron proteins (FePs) and FeSII, in which FeSII mediates interactions with MoFeP and FeP to position their FeS clusters in catalytically inactive but O2-protected states.
